**What the rules actually state:**
According to the gov.uk guidance on Child Benefit when children are in hospital, if a child returns to hospital within **28 days** of leaving, the hospital stays are "linked" and count cumulatively toward the 12-week limit. This is the "Linking Rule" mentioned in the scenario.

