- First hospital stay: 10 weeks
- Home period: 2 weeks (14 days)
- Arthur returned to hospital: 15 days after discharge (within the 28-day linking period)
- Second hospital stay: 3 weeks
- **Cumulative total: 10 + 3 = 13 weeks**

